function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

@set_time_limit(0);

@header('Content-Type: text/plain');

chdir(__DIR__);
if (trim(@file_get_contents('oidplus_version.txt')) !== 'Revision 3') {
	err('This update can only be applied to OIDplus version 2.0.0.3!');
}

if (version_compare(PHP_VERSION, '7.0.0') < 0) {
	err('You need PHP Version 7.0 to update to this version');
}

// File added: .user.ini
function writefile_1() {
	@$fp = fopen('.user.ini', 'w');
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('ZGVmYXVsdF9jaGFyc2V0ID0gInV0Zi04Igo='));
	@fclose($fp);
}
if (is_file('.user.ini') && (sha1_file('.user.ini') != 'fb5b7c8554120af9f48a63700633d1bbc97ae6e5')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: .user.ini');
	$tmp = pathinfo('.user.ini');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('.user.ini')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('.user.ini', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_1();
if (!is_file('.user.ini')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): .user.ini');
} else if (sha1_file('.user.ini') != 'fb5b7c8554120af9f48a63700633d1bbc97ae6e5') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): .user.ini');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('.user.ini', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of .user.ini');
}

// Dir added: 3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/js
@mkdir('3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/js');
if (!is_dir('3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/js')) {
	warn('Directory could not be created: 3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/js');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/js', 0755)) {
	warn('Could not change directory permissions of 3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/js');
}

	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/js/emojis.js');
	$tmp = pathinfo('3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/js/emojis.js');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/js/emojis.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/js/emojis.js', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}

if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/js/emojis.js')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/js/emojis.js');
} else if (sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/js/emojis.js') != '87285a6406baeee48ff9a1def4824075e7cc6298') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/js/emojis.js');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/js/emojis.js', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/js/emojis.js');
}

	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/js/emojis.min.js');
	$tmp = pathinfo('3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/js/emojis.min.js');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/js/emojis.min.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/js/emojis.min.js', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}

	if (!@copy('3p/tinymce/skins/ui/oxide-dark/content.inline.min.css', $backup_name)) {

if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/jquery.tinymce.min.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: 3p/tinymce/jquery.tinymce.min.js');
	writefile_19();
	if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/jquery.tinymce.min.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/tinymce/jquery.tinymce.min.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/tinymce/jquery.tinymce.min.js') != '28ac0571fc2deb23615a5efd76a4d81db7fd151f') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/jquery.tinymce.min.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/tinymce/jquery.tinymce.min.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/tinymce/jquery.tinymce.min.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/jquery.tinymce.min.js') !== '28ac0571fc2deb23615a5efd76a4d81db7fd151f') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/jquery.tinymce.min.js') !== 'd7e55b36b5a17a9421bf41df697caf85f567cb28') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/tinymce/jquery.tinymce.min.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/tinymce/jquery.tinymce.min.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/tinymce/jquery.tinymce.min.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/tinymce/jquery.tinymce.min.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_19();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/jquery.tinymce.min.js') !== '28ac0571fc2deb23615a5efd76a4d81db7fd151f') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/jquery.tinymce.min.js');
		}
	}
}

	writefile_28();

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/tinymce/plugins/codesample/plugin.min.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/codesample/plugin.min.js') != 'd2e28da18ace46bfa315ccb444bb269e6f8946f9') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/codesample/plugin.min.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/tinymce/plugins/codesample/plugin.min.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/tinymce/plugins/codesample/plugin.min.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/codesample/plugin.min.js') !== 'd2e28da18ace46bfa315ccb444bb269e6f8946f9') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/codesample/plugin.min.js') !== '9820c99e8fcec860abf25d0f0319aa234db6b5c0') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/tinymce/plugins/codesample/plugin.min.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/tinymce/plugins/codesample/plugin.min.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/tinymce/plugins/codesample/plugin.min.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/tinymce/plugins/codesample/plugin.min.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_28();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/codesample/plugin.min.js') !== 'd2e28da18ace46bfa315ccb444bb269e6f8946f9') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/codesample/plugin.min.js');

if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/plugin.min.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: 3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/plugin.min.js');
	writefile_32();
	if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/plugin.min.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/plugin.min.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/plugin.min.js') != 'ec0fe112dc3dd50fdeb47222ea09e3a03992e465') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/plugin.min.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/plugin.min.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/plugin.min.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/plugin.min.js') !== 'ec0fe112dc3dd50fdeb47222ea09e3a03992e465') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/plugin.min.js') !== '954a326ce29c54b1ac760695c7c034705637e059') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/plugin.min.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/plugin.min.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/plugin.min.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/plugin.min.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_32();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/plugin.min.js') !== 'ec0fe112dc3dd50fdeb47222ea09e3a03992e465') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/emoticons/plugin.min.js');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/tinymce/plugins/fullpage/plugin.min.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/fullpage/plugin.min.js') != '453cb2e141bddecfdc8838be5b550f8512e2c18a') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/fullpage/plugin.min.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/tinymce/plugins/fullpage/plugin.min.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/tinymce/plugins/fullpage/plugin.min.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/fullpage/plugin.min.js') !== '453cb2e141bddecfdc8838be5b550f8512e2c18a') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/fullpage/plugin.min.js') !== '238fc4e04ee4b1ca6946d76fb2a07a99464e2847') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/tinymce/plugins/fullpage/plugin.min.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/tinymce/plugins/fullpage/plugin.min.js');

				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}

if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/image/plugin.min.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: 3p/tinymce/plugins/image/plugin.min.js');
	writefile_37();
	if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/image/plugin.min.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/tinymce/plugins/image/plugin.min.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/image/plugin.min.js') != '9a984ee886ac9a30fbd3ad9e69d160b381b34e75') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/image/plugin.min.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/tinymce/plugins/image/plugin.min.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/tinymce/plugins/image/plugin.min.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/image/plugin.min.js') !== '9a984ee886ac9a30fbd3ad9e69d160b381b34e75') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/image/plugin.min.js') !== '7d831e184602458f78e87b9d02fe1ff77f1d6d55') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/tinymce/plugins/image/plugin.min.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/tinymce/plugins/image/plugin.min.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/tinymce/plugins/image/plugin.min.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/tinymce/plugins/image/plugin.min.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_37();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/image/plugin.min.js') !== '9a984ee886ac9a30fbd3ad9e69d160b381b34e75') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/image/plugin.min.js');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/link/plugin.min.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: 3p/tinymce/plugins/link/plugin.min.js');
	writefile_42();
	if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/link/plugin.min.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/tinymce/plugins/link/plugin.min.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/link/plugin.min.js') != '9bd2f22ff3db06ffc7f9537791c8ddd29bdcd1aa') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/link/plugin.min.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/tinymce/plugins/link/plugin.min.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/tinymce/plugins/link/plugin.min.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/link/plugin.min.js') !== '9bd2f22ff3db06ffc7f9537791c8ddd29bdcd1aa') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/link/plugin.min.js') !== '6144ebad91f60b2934de461851c8f38da2e1de40') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/tinymce/plugins/link/plugin.min.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/tinymce/plugins/link/plugin.min.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/tinymce/plugins/link/plugin.min.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/tinymce/plugins/link/plugin.min.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_42();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/link/plugin.min.js') !== '9bd2f22ff3db06ffc7f9537791c8ddd29bdcd1aa') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/link/plugin.min.js');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/lists/plugin.min.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: 3p/tinymce/plugins/lists/plugin.min.js');
	writefile_43();
	if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/lists/plugin.min.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/tinymce/plugins/lists/plugin.min.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/lists/plugin.min.js') != 'bc96bcbe0ee116dc2cb2c58ea78bfd33503d4da5') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/lists/plugin.min.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/tinymce/plugins/lists/plugin.min.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/tinymce/plugins/lists/plugin.min.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/lists/plugin.min.js') !== 'bc96bcbe0ee116dc2cb2c58ea78bfd33503d4da5') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/lists/plugin.min.js') !== 'e925c1ce04c7e61376f1e789ac99fa7b73d1232f') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/tinymce/plugins/lists/plugin.min.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/tinymce/plugins/lists/plugin.min.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/tinymce/plugins/lists/plugin.min.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/tinymce/plugins/lists/plugin.min.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_43();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/lists/plugin.min.js') !== 'bc96bcbe0ee116dc2cb2c58ea78bfd33503d4da5') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/lists/plugin.min.js');
		}
	}
}

		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/save/plugin.min.js') !== 'af6f4d994aba0e9724c72026d057a7213ab664e0') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/save/plugin.min.js');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/searchreplace/plugin.min.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: 3p/tinymce/plugins/searchreplace/plugin.min.js');
	writefile_52();
	if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/searchreplace/plugin.min.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/tinymce/plugins/searchreplace/plugin.min.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/searchreplace/plugin.min.js') != 'f6082815e7b7674b9af6e851302e7492cda00bf6') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/searchreplace/plugin.min.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/tinymce/plugins/searchreplace/plugin.min.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/tinymce/plugins/searchreplace/plugin.min.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/searchreplace/plugin.min.js') !== 'f6082815e7b7674b9af6e851302e7492cda00bf6') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/searchreplace/plugin.min.js') !== 'e020a3f626955a03be5d68e0e581bf9ce3702bd4') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/tinymce/plugins/searchreplace/plugin.min.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/tinymce/plugins/searchreplace/plugin.min.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/tinymce/plugins/searchreplace/plugin.min.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/tinymce/plugins/searchreplace/plugin.min.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_52();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/searchreplace/plugin.min.js') !== 'f6082815e7b7674b9af6e851302e7492cda00bf6') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/searchreplace/plugin.min.js');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/spellchecker/plugin.min.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: 3p/tinymce/plugins/spellchecker/plugin.min.js');
	writefile_53();
	if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/spellchecker/plugin.min.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/tinymce/plugins/spellchecker/plugin.min.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/spellchecker/plugin.min.js') != 'f93b4f8f809cfd3faa23e053bb9456f70470cb56') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/spellchecker/plugin.min.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/tinymce/plugins/spellchecker/plugin.min.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/tinymce/plugins/spellchecker/plugin.min.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/spellchecker/plugin.min.js') !== 'f93b4f8f809cfd3faa23e053bb9456f70470cb56') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/spellchecker/plugin.min.js') !== 'e0553afd926baf8c72d41ad04e0106c18400f508') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/tinymce/plugins/spellchecker/plugin.min.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/tinymce/plugins/spellchecker/plugin.min.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/tinymce/plugins/spellchecker/plugin.min.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/tinymce/plugins/spellchecker/plugin.min.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_53();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/spellchecker/plugin.min.js') !== 'f93b4f8f809cfd3faa23e053bb9456f70470cb56') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/spellchecker/plugin.min.js');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/tabfocus/plugin.min.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: 3p/tinymce/plugins/tabfocus/plugin.min.js');
	writefile_54();
	if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/tabfocus/plugin.min.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/tinymce/plugins/tabfocus/plugin.min.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/tabfocus/plugin.min.js') != 'e8ac6147c337ce0012f2434d35023d98ba51bb56') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/tabfocus/plugin.min.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/tinymce/plugins/tabfocus/plugin.min.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/tinymce/plugins/tabfocus/plugin.min.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/tabfocus/plugin.min.js') !== 'e8ac6147c337ce0012f2434d35023d98ba51bb56') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/tabfocus/plugin.min.js') !== 'bf12c77b109b4099e1b3e5822d213affa62aff92') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/tinymce/plugins/tabfocus/plugin.min.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/tinymce/plugins/tabfocus/plugin.min.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/tinymce/plugins/tabfocus/plugin.min.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/tinymce/plugins/tabfocus/plugin.min.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_54();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/tabfocus/plugin.min.js') !== 'e8ac6147c337ce0012f2434d35023d98ba51bb56') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/tabfocus/plugin.min.js');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/tinymce/plugins/table/plugin.min.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/table/plugin.min.js') != '7c47053b714dc2819599490c590f47810e360c87') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/table/plugin.min.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/tinymce/plugins/table/plugin.min.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/tinymce/plugins/table/plugin.min.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/table/plugin.min.js') !== '7c47053b714dc2819599490c590f47810e360c87') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/table/plugin.min.js') !== '24c380bca5836a1684bc493853de9ffe25e04d53') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/tinymce/plugins/table/plugin.min.js');

			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/tinymce/plugins/table/plugin.min.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_55();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/table/plugin.min.js') !== '7c47053b714dc2819599490c590f47810e360c87') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/table/plugin.min.js');

if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/template/plugin.min.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: 3p/tinymce/plugins/template/plugin.min.js');
	writefile_56();
	if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/template/plugin.min.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/tinymce/plugins/template/plugin.min.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/template/plugin.min.js') != '639ec944c60858e24346ab8018580f928adee07a') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/template/plugin.min.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/tinymce/plugins/template/plugin.min.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/tinymce/plugins/template/plugin.min.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/template/plugin.min.js') !== '639ec944c60858e24346ab8018580f928adee07a') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/template/plugin.min.js') !== '57c37584bb0bf31369a34ce11a9813c37a07894e') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/tinymce/plugins/template/plugin.min.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/tinymce/plugins/template/plugin.min.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/tinymce/plugins/template/plugin.min.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/tinymce/plugins/template/plugin.min.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_56();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/template/plugin.min.js') !== '639ec944c60858e24346ab8018580f928adee07a') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/template/plugin.min.js');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/textcolor/plugin.min.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: 3p/tinymce/plugins/textcolor/plugin.min.js');
	writefile_57();
	if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/textcolor/plugin.min.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/tinymce/plugins/textcolor/plugin.min.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/textcolor/plugin.min.js') != 'a4b6ea193669159b0d9c15668583bd6c361ab006') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/textcolor/plugin.min.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/tinymce/plugins/textcolor/plugin.min.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/tinymce/plugins/textcolor/plugin.min.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/textcolor/plugin.min.js') !== 'a4b6ea193669159b0d9c15668583bd6c361ab006') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/textcolor/plugin.min.js') !== 'c62971d366687921124a0c464caeb59a27f4e44d') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/tinymce/plugins/textcolor/plugin.min.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/tinymce/plugins/textcolor/plugin.min.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/tinymce/plugins/textcolor/plugin.min.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/tinymce/plugins/textcolor/plugin.min.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_57();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/textcolor/plugin.min.js') !== 'a4b6ea193669159b0d9c15668583bd6c361ab006') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/textcolor/plugin.min.js');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/visualchars/plugin.min.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: 3p/tinymce/plugins/visualchars/plugin.min.js');
	writefile_61();
	if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/visualchars/plugin.min.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/tinymce/plugins/visualchars/plugin.min.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/visualchars/plugin.min.js') != 'f69a7816514575e6437cff6f38684a8cb0a4c879') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/visualchars/plugin.min.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/tinymce/plugins/visualchars/plugin.min.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/tinymce/plugins/visualchars/plugin.min.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/visualchars/plugin.min.js') !== 'f69a7816514575e6437cff6f38684a8cb0a4c879') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/visualchars/plugin.min.js') !== '73643d396b017a7d03fc8794833e02f42c045ccb') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/tinymce/plugins/visualchars/plugin.min.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/tinymce/plugins/visualchars/plugin.min.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/tinymce/plugins/visualchars/plugin.min.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/tinymce/plugins/visualchars/plugin.min.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_61();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/visualchars/plugin.min.js') !== 'f69a7816514575e6437cff6f38684a8cb0a4c879') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/visualchars/plugin.min.js');
		}
	}
}

	}

	if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/wordcount/plugin.min.js') !== '3ee8e1d4af7130f80a5e421d9f7111ad38da0165') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/wordcount/plugin.min.js') !== 'bd5253ebc5665692b55ba20d0e94745238eec602') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/tinymce/plugins/wordcount/plugin.min.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/tinymce/plugins/wordcount/plugin.min.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/tinymce/plugins/wordcount/plugin.min.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/tinymce/plugins/wordcount/plugin.min.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_62();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/plugins/wordcount/plugin.min.js') !== '3ee8e1d4af7130f80a5e421d9f7111ad38da0165') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/plugins/wordcount/plugin.min.js');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/themes/mobile/theme.min.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: 3p/tinymce/themes/mobile/theme.min.js');
	writefile_63();
	if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/themes/mobile/theme.min.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/tinymce/themes/mobile/theme.min.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/tinymce/themes/mobile/theme.min.js') != 'ccad85ad77436eda91d3bb7fc505b15d078d5a2a') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/themes/mobile/theme.min.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/tinymce/themes/mobile/theme.min.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/tinymce/themes/mobile/theme.min.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/themes/mobile/theme.min.js') !== 'ccad85ad77436eda91d3bb7fc505b15d078d5a2a') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/themes/mobile/theme.min.js') !== '918fd872f100380bc8934ae4292cc413f6ca1dbd') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/tinymce/themes/mobile/theme.min.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/tinymce/themes/mobile/theme.min.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/tinymce/themes/mobile/theme.min.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/tinymce/themes/mobile/theme.min.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_63();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/themes/mobile/theme.min.js') !== 'ccad85ad77436eda91d3bb7fc505b15d078d5a2a') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/themes/mobile/theme.min.js');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/tinymce.min.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: 3p/tinymce/tinymce.min.js');
	writefile_64();
	if (!is_file('3p/tinymce/tinymce.min.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): 3p/tinymce/tinymce.min.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('3p/tinymce/tinymce.min.js') != '3aea39c225c5ffda70c4fdae37d1877290906927') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/tinymce.min.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('3p/tinymce/tinymce.min.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of 3p/tinymce/tinymce.min.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/tinymce.min.js') !== '3aea39c225c5ffda70c4fdae37d1877290906927') {
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/tinymce.min.js') !== '48c044adc0c7944c30644310fbf4ef0de02ec829') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: 3p/tinymce/tinymce.min.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('3p/tinymce/tinymce.min.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('3p/tinymce/tinymce.min.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('3p/tinymce/tinymce.min.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_64();
		if (@sha1_file('3p/tinymce/tinymce.min.js') !== '3aea39c225c5ffda70c4fdae37d1877290906927') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): 3p/tinymce/tinymce.min.js');
		}
	}
}

			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_67();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php') !== 'dbbfa7a5c3a9085d44f897111aff3956a51d6971') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/oidinfo_api.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/oidinfo_api.inc.php');
	writefile_68();
	if (!is_file('includes/oidinfo_api.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/oidinfo_api.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/oidinfo_api.inc.php') != '342c55335c972564209f791b6fd95a1ebad65f68') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/oidinfo_api.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/oidinfo_api.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/oidinfo_api.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/oidinfo_api.inc.php') !== '342c55335c972564209f791b6fd95a1ebad65f68') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/oidinfo_api.inc.php') !== 'c967760786db6331f520127ed7fdc004479b3ab9') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/oidinfo_api.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/oidinfo_api.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/oidinfo_api.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/oidinfo_api.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_68();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/oidinfo_api.inc.php') !== '342c55335c972564209f791b6fd95a1ebad65f68') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/oidinfo_api.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('index.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: index.php');
	writefile_69();
	if (!is_file('index.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): index.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('index.php') != 'cacf1c33f3a109ae44839e5f756d372422fef700') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): index.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('index.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of index.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('index.php') !== 'cacf1c33f3a109ae44839e5f756d372422fef700') {
		if (@sha1_file('index.php') !== 'b3dbbd7b298b8b975ebed5a4c20910809553569f') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: index.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('index.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('index.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('index.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_69();
		if (@sha1_file('index.php') !== 'cacf1c33f3a109ae44839e5f756d372422fef700') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): index.php');
		}
	}
}

	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('dmVyICovCgljb2xvcjogIzAwOTsKfQoKLyogbWFza3MgYXJlIHVzdWFsbHkgdHJhbnNwYXJlbnQgLSBtYWtlIHRoZW0gdmlzaWJsZSAobXVzdCAnb3ZlcnJpZGUnIGRlZmF1bHQpICovCi51aS1sYXlvdXQtbWFzayB7CgliYWNrZ3JvdW5kOgkjQzAwICFpbXBvcnRh'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('bnQ7CglvcGFjaXR5OgkuMjAgIWltcG9ydGFudDsKCWZpbHRlcjoJCWFscGhhKG9wYWNpdHk9MjApICFpbXBvcnRhbnQ7Cn0K'));
	@fclose($fp);
}
if (!is_file('oidplus.css')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: oidplus.css');
	writefile_70();
	if (!is_file('oidplus.css')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): oidplus.css');
	} else if (sha1_file('oidplus.css') != 'dd402213e08d384fe3c3f7762e66fad1057b9c08') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): oidplus.css');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('oidplus.css', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of oidplus.css');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('oidplus.css') !== 'dd402213e08d384fe3c3f7762e66fad1057b9c08') {
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus.css') !== '052381d38746e569b3a4984fc489cae3db548257') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: oidplus.css');
			$tmp = pathinfo('oidplus.css');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('oidplus.css')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('oidplus.css', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_70();
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus.css') !== 'dd402213e08d384fe3c3f7762e66fad1057b9c08') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): oidplus.css');
		}
	}
}

	@fclose($fp);
}
if (!is_file('oidplus.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: oidplus.js');
	writefile_71();
	if (!is_file('oidplus.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): oidplus.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('oidplus.js') != '5a1e3ad9cf97ba2a2583aac335893b6d77109683') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): oidplus.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('oidplus.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of oidplus.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('oidplus.js') !== '5a1e3ad9cf97ba2a2583aac335893b6d77109683') {
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus.js') !== 'fef3433595dcbc0c8028832ee69687c5036bc8d1') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: oidplus.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('oidplus.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('oidplus.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('oidplus.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_71();
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus.js') !== '5a1e3ad9cf97ba2a2583aac335893b6d77109683') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): oidplus.js');
		}
	}
}


file_put_contents('oidplus_version.txt', "Revision 4\n");
if (trim(@file_get_contents('oidplus_version.txt')) !== 'Revision 4') err('Could not write to oidplus_version.txt!');


echo 'DONE'; // This exact string will be compared in Update v3

@unlink(__FILE__);
if (is_file(__FILE__)) warn('Could not delete '.basename(__FILE__).'! Please delete it manually');
